<br>
If this works out it will be a great addition to the server - less arguments and more happy clerics works for me. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  If anyone needs a 55 shaman's help with Rage then feel free to send me a tell and I'll do my best to come along. I may even drag some of DoSG along to protect me. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  I would hope that all guilds honour this list and do not KS. The rules may not support such a camp rota, but there is nothing to say that a server can't come together to make up their own rules once in a while. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><HTML>

